name: Season 19 (Mouse/Keyboard)

data.description:
Tunnel Vision grants the following for 6 seconds after a Reload from a kill for 5 seconds: +20 AIM Assist, -20% Accuracy Cone Size, ADS Handling x 2.

Repulsor Brace grants 45HP Overshield on Void-debuffed kill.

Handling on Master.

It should be noted that the proc chance on Veist Stinger has different ranges auto rifle/smg/scout rifle has a 2% chance to proc, sidearm has a 4% chance to proc, and bow/lfr has a 10% chance to proc.

Currently, Kill Clip is bugged and doesn't Activate on Kill.

It should be noted that the proc chance on Veist Stinger has different ranges auto rifle/smg/scout rifle has a 2% chance to proc, sidearm has a 4% chance to proc, and bow/lfr has a 10% chance to proc.

Currently, Kill Clip is bugged and doesn't Activate on Kill.

Killing Wind grants the following for 5 seconds, and is refreshed to 5 seconds after each kill to a max of 8 seconds: +20 Range, 50 Mobility, 40 Handling, +30% reduced ADS movement penalty, +5% increased damage falloff.

Repulsor Brace grants 45HP Overshield on Void-debuffed kill.

Range on Master.
Armor Piercing boosts damage by 5%, Range +5, and penetrates the target shield.
